author: Taegan Goddard
title: Trump Maintains National Lead in New Poll
text:
Trump Maintains National Lead in New Poll October 26, 2015 
A new Morning Consult poll finds Donald Trump leading the GOP president field nationally with 35%m, followed by Ben Carson at 20%, Jeb Bush at 8%, Marco Rubio at 6% and Mike Huckabee at 4%.
